description: Gets latest heatmap for Traffic Manager profile.

profile_name.description: The name of the Traffic Manager profile.

heat_map_type.description: The type of HeatMap for the Traffic Manager profile.

top_left.description: The top left latitude,longitude pair of the rectangular viewport to query for.

bot_right.description: The bottom right latitude,longitude pair of the rectangular viewport to query for.

subscription_id.description: Gets subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group containing the Traffic Manager endpoint.
